window.docContents[50].resolve({"/Basic-Types/Natural-Numbers/#nat-api-elim":{"contents":"为 Nat 自动生成的递归原理会产生以 Nat.zero 和 Nat.succ 表述的证明目标。\n这对于用户来说不是特别友好，因此提供了另一种逻辑等效的递归原则，其结果是用 0 和 n + 1 来表述的目标。\n自定义消除器 用于 induction 和 cases策略可以使用 induction_eliminator 和 cases_eliminator 属性提供。\n\nA recursor for Nat that uses the notations 0 for Nat.zero and n + 1 for Nat.succ.It is otherwise identical to the default recursor Nat.rec. It is used by the induction tactic\nby default for Nat.\n\nA case analysis principle for Nat that uses the notations 0 for Nat.zero and n + 1 for\nNat.succ.It is otherwise identical to the default recursor Nat.casesOn. It is used as the default Nat\ncase analysis principle for Nat by the cases tactic.\n\n\n\n","context":"Lean 参考\u0009基本类型\u0009自然数\u0009API 参考","header":"20.1.4.8. 消除","id":"/Basic-Types/Natural-Numbers/#nat-api-elim"},"/Basic-Types/Strings/#zh-basictypes-string-slice-h008":{"contents":"Obtains the smallest valid position that is greater than or equal to the given byte position.\n\nObtains the smallest valid position that is strictly greater than the given byte position.\n\n","context":"Lean 参考\u0009基本类型\u0009弦乐\u0009API 参考\u0009字符串切片\u0009API 参考","header":"20.8.4.11.1.6. 职位","id":"/Basic-Types/Strings/#zh-basictypes-string-slice-h008"},"/Basic-Types/Strings/#zh-basictypes-string-slice-h017":{"contents":"Returns the previous valid position before the given position, given a proof that the position\nis not the start position, which guarantees that such a position exists.\n\nReturns the previous valid position before the given position, or panics if the position is\nthe start position.\n\nReturns the previous valid position before the given position, or none if the position is\nthe start position.\n\nIterates p.prev n times.If this would move p past the start of s, the result is s.endPos.\n\nAdvances a valid position on a slice to the next valid position, given a proof that the\nposition is not the past-the-end position, which guarantees that such a position exists.\n\nAdvances a valid position on a slice to the next valid position, or panics if the given\nposition is the past-the-end position.\n\nAdvances a valid position on a slice to the next valid position, or returns none if the\ngiven position is the past-the-end position.\n\nAdvances the position p n times.If this would move p past the end of s, the result is s.endPos.\n\n","context":"Lean 参考\u0009基本类型\u0009弦乐\u0009API 参考\u0009字符串切片\u0009职位","header":"20.8.4.11.3.2. 递增和递减","id":"/Basic-Types/Strings/#zh-basictypes-string-slice-h017"},"/Terms/Functions/#function-terms":{"contents":"具有函数类型的术语可以通过抽象创建，通过 fun 关键字引入。在各个社区中，函数抽象也称为 lambdas，因为 Alonzo Church 对它们的表示法，或者称为匿名函数，因为它们不需要在全局环境中使用名称进行定义。\n虽然核心 类型论 中的抽象仅允许绑定单个变量，但函数术语在高级 Lean 语法中非常灵活。\n\nFunction Abstraction最基本的函数抽象引入一个变量来代表函数的参数：在精化时间，Lean 必须能够确定函数的域。\n类型归属是提供此信息的一种方式：\n\n使用 def desugar 到 fun 等关键字定义的函数定义。\n另一方面，归纳类型声明引入了具有函数类型（构造函数和类型构造函数）的新值，这些值本身不能仅使用 fun 来实现。\n\nCurried Functionsfun 之后接受多个参数名称：多个参数的不同类型注释需要括号：这些相当于编写嵌套的 fun 项。\n\n在本节中描述的所有语法中，=> 可以替换为 ↦。\n\n函数抽象还可以使用模式匹配语法作为其参数规范的一部分，从而避免需要引入立即解构的局部变量。\n有关模式匹配的部分中描述了此语法。\n\n\n\n","context":"Lean 参考\u0009条款","header":"13.3. 功能","id":"/Terms/Functions/#function-terms"},"/releases/v4.28.1/#release-v4___28___1":{"contents":"此版本有 2 处更改。\n除了 0 个功能添加之外，\n以及下面列出的 1 个修复，\n有 0 处重构更改，\n0 项文档改进，\n0 性能改进，\n对测试套件进行 0 项改进，\n以及其他 1 项变更。\n\n\n\n","context":"Lean 参考\u0009发行说明","header":"Lean 4.28.1 (2026-04-14)","id":"/releases/v4.28.1/#release-v4___28___1"},"/releases/v4.29.0/#release-v4___29___0":{"contents":"此版本有 453 项更改。除了下面列出的 112 项功能添加和 107 项修复之外，还有 30 项重构更改、21 项文档改进、29 项性能改进、26 项测试套件改进和 115 项其他更改。\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n","context":"Lean 参考\u0009发行说明","header":"Lean 4.29.0 (2026-03-27)","id":"/releases/v4.29.0/#release-v4___29___0"}});